                    <span>This is an excellent book for those who have some working knowledge of Nepali and the Devnagri script. It is dense, but well organized. The book alone may be a bit daunting for beginners.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A complete guide to learning Nepali</div>
